Package: project
Type: Package
Title: Recipe Search & Simulation 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Guo 
Maintainer: David Guo <davidguo@umich.edu>
Contributer: David Guo
Description: The package contains three functions. 
    Recipe Search contains a function that uses the Recipe Puppy API 
    to return 100 recipes given a list of ingredients. Simulation 
    consists of two functions that look at assumption violation with
    the errors for linear regression and plots various combinations
    of parameters and estimates.
